OL,3,CUK bans fake reviews and hidden online
OL,4,Cshopping fees under new law
OL,6,FA new law that bans fake reviews and
OL,7,Fhidden online shopping fees has now
OL,8,Fcome into force, as ITV News' Caroline
OL,9,FLewis reports
OL,11,FFake reviews and so-called drip
OL,12,Fpricing for online shopping are banned
OL,13,Funder a new law that comes into force
OL,14,Ffrom Sunday.
OL,16,FAdministration fees and ticking
OL,17,Fbooking fees must now be included in
OL,18,Fthe headline price but the law does
OL,19,Fnot cover optional fees such as
OL,20,Fairline seats and baggage upgrades for
OL,21,Fflights.
