OL,3,CUK bans fake reviews and hidden online
OL,4,Cshopping fees under new law
OL,6,FGoing forward, online platforms will,
OL,7,Fby law, have to take steps to prevent
OL,8,Fand remove fake consumer reviews from
OL,9,Ftheir websites.
OL,11,FConsumers spend #2.2 billion on hidden
OL,12,Ffees every year, according to the
OL,13,FDepartment for Business and Trade.
OL,15,FJustin Madders, minister for
OL,16,Fcompetition and markets, said: "From
OL,17,Ftoday consumers can confidently make
OL,18,Fpurchases knowing they are protected
OL,19,Fagainst fake reviews and dripped
OL,20,Fpricing.
