OL,6,F"These changes will give consumers
OL,7,Fmore power and control over their hard-
OL,8,Fearned cash, as well as help to
OL,9,Festablish a level playing field by
OL,10,Fdeterring bad actors that undercut
OL,11,Fcompliant businesses."
OL,13,FThe measures come under the Digital
OL,14,FMarkets, Competition and Consumers
OL,15,FBill approved by Parliament last year.
